reviewText: Very beautiful anime. Arrived in mint condition.
Totally worth the purchase; subtitles are some of the best in the biz, dub is crisp and meets standards, and the bumped up audio quality is a nice touch that the I.P. definitely deserves.

I am a Japanese but I like dubbed English anime.
Dubbed English is so cool, also it can change Japanese language.
Great story worth it. But i have seen it 30$ less
That's interesting!! I have never seen anime like this before.
